#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Pañcālacaṇḍasutta"
msgstr "7. With Pañcālacaṇḍa"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.7:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn2.7:1.2"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho pañcālacaṇḍo devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ "
"abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, the god Pañcālacaṇḍa recited this verse in the Buddha’"
"s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.7:2.1"
msgid "“Sambādhe vata okāsaṃ,"
msgstr "“The opening amid confinement"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.7:2.2"
msgid "Avindi bhūrimedhaso;"
msgstr "was discovered by the Buddha of vast intelligence,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: jhānamabujjhi → jhānamabudhā (bj, pts2) | jhānamabuddhi (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn2.7:2.3"
msgid "Yo jhānamabujjhi buddho,"
msgstr "who woke up to absorption,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.7:2.4"
msgid "Paṭilīnanisabho munī”ti."
msgstr "the sage, the solitary bull.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.111"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.7:3.1"
msgid "“Sambādhe vāpi vindanti, (pañcālacaṇḍāti bhagavā)"
msgstr "“Even amid confinement they discover,” said the Buddha to Pañcālacaṇḍa,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.7:3.2"
msgid "Dhammaṃ nibbānapattiyā;"
msgstr "“the principle for attaining extinguishment."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.7:3.3"
msgid "Ye satiṃ paccalatthaṃsu,"
msgstr "Those who have acquired mindfulness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.7:3.4"
msgid "Sammā te susamāhitā”ti."
msgstr "are perfectly serene in samādhi.”"
